    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🟥🟥🟥🟧🟧🟧🟨🟨🟨🟩🟩🟩🟦🟦🟦🟪🟪🟪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578290/extras/dd8b6aec72ce41069658fa7ca48bd784.poster.avif?t=1763121964\" width=478 height=44 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578290/extras/dd8b6aec72ce41069658fa7ca48bd784.webm?t=1763121964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578290/extras/dd8b6aec72ce41069658fa7ca48bd784.mp4?t=1763121964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >停留片刻，放松一下！Pixel Fixel 承诺提供尽可能多的放松色彩匹配游戏体验！没有应用内购买、广告或任何其他花招！完全免费，完全有益！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家的任务是恢复混合色渐变到它的前一状态！这有助于训练玩家对色彩的敏感度，并提供一种舒缓而充实的感觉。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受数百个级别</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创建你自己的级别</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在在线 1 对 1 比赛中与你的朋友对战。解谜最快的人获胜！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🟥🟥🟥🟧🟧🟧🟨🟨🟨🟩🟩🟩🟦🟦🟦🟪🟪🟪</p>",
